    <h2 class="section-title deep-lavender has-text-centered">Ecosystem overview</h2>
    <h3 class="dark-indigo has-text-centered">Every stakeholder benefits from collective value creation through development of Ecosystem V</h3>
        <div class="columns is-vcentered">
